<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.8.7">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://chenxuan353.github.io/tweetToQQbot/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://chenxuan353.github.io/tweetToQQbot/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2020-06-05T22:38:24+08:00</updated><id>https://chenxuan353.github.io/tweetToQQbot/atom.xml</id><title type="html">tweetToQQbot 使用文档</title><subtitle>The Documentation Site for tweetToQQbot Project</subtitle><author><name>Chen Xuan &amp; Cyame</name></author><entry><title type="html">Next Theme Tutorial</title><link href="https://chenxuan353.github.io/tweetToQQbot/tutorial/2017/07/20/next-tutorial/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Next Theme Tutorial" /><published>2017-07-20T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2017-07-20T00:00:00+08:00</updated><id>https://chenxuan353.github.io/tweetToQQbot/tutorial/2017/07/20/next-tutorial</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://chenxuan353.github.io/tweetToQQbot/tutorial/2017/07/20/next-tutorial/">&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;NexT is a high quality elegant &lt;a href=&quot;https://jekyllrb.com&quot;&gt;Jekyll&lt;/a&gt; theme ported from &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next&quot;&gt;Hexo Next&lt;/a&gt;. It is crafted from scratch, with love.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;!-- more --&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://simpleyyt.github.io/jekyll-theme-next/&quot;&gt;Live Preview&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

